CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

June 25, 2014

[Cite as 06/25/2014 Case Announcements, 2014-Ohio-2725.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2013- 2027. Thomas v. Neal.

In Habeas Corpus. On petition for writ of habeas corpus of James Thomas. Sua sponte, cause dismissed. On motion for a ruling. Motion denied as moot.

O’Connor, C.J., and Pfeifer, O’Donnell, Lanzinger, Kennedy, French, and O’Neill, JJ., concur.
